trans-unit.source: Represents an immutable (read-only) pair of "Name" and "Description" strings.
trans-unit.target: Representa um par imutável (somente leitura) de cadeias de caracteres de "Nome" e "Descrição".

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair> is a basic building block for structures that express locale specific information for an <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UnsignedPublishLicense>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair> é um bloco de construção básico para estruturas que informações específicas da localidade express para uma <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.UnsignedPublishLicense>.

trans-unit.source: The value for the locale <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> property.
trans-unit.target: O valor para a propriedade <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> da localidade.

trans-unit.source: The value for the locale <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> property.
trans-unit.target: O valor para a propriedade <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> da localidade.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />.

trans-unit.source: Either the <paramref name="name" /> parameter or <paramref name="description" /> parameter is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: O parâmetro <paramref name="name" /> ou o parâmetro <paramref name="description" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description%2A> property is set as a parameter to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description%2A> propriedade é definida como um parâmetro para o <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> construtor.

trans-unit.source: The object to compare the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of.
trans-unit.target: O objeto cujas propriedades <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> e <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> comparar.

trans-unit.source: Indicates whether the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of a given object match those of this <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />.
trans-unit.target: Indica se as propriedades <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> e <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> de um determinado objeto correspondem àquelas deste <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of the given object match those of this instance; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se as propriedades <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> e <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> do objeto fornecido corresponderem àquelas desta instância; caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets a computed hash code based on the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um código hash calculado baseado nas propriedades <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> e <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" />.

trans-unit.source: A computed hash code based on the <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> and <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> properties of this <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />.
trans-unit.target: Um código hash calculado baseado nas propriedades <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name" /> e <see cref="P:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Description" /> deste <see cref="T:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name%2A> property is set as a parameter to the <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> constructor.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.Name%2A> propriedade é definida como um parâmetro para o <xref:System.Security.RightsManagement.LocalizedNameDescriptionPair.%23ctor%2A> construtor.
